g.aria-label: Hackadrone 2018 was India's first UAV Hackathon conducted by Cyient, Microsoft and the Government of Telangana. I developed an autonomous women security drone network which when summoned through an app, live streams the victim to the police and victim's family. My implementation of this project bagged the first prize.
